Puppet module: resolv_conf

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages resolv_conf software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include resolv_conf              # Install and run resolv_conf with standard configurations.
include resolv_conf::disable     # Disable resolv_conf service.
include resolv_conf::disableboot # Disable resolv_conf service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include resolv_conf::absent      # Remove resolv_conf package.

DEPENDENCIES:
